OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOver-50s encouraged to end 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fearly retirement           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government is considering plans to 
OL,6, coax retired middle-aged workers back  
OL,7, into jobs to boost the economy.        
OL,9,FOlder people who have given up work    
OL,10,Fcould be offered what is being dubbed a
OL,11,F"midlife MoT" to entice them back into 
OL,12,Femployment, the Times reports.         
OL,14,FThe paper says the MoT would assess    
OL,15,Ffinances and opportunities for work.   
OL,17,FIt follows a recent House of Lords     
OL,18,Fcommittee finding that a wave of early 
OL,19,Fretirement following the pandemic has  
OL,20,Fcaused a huge labour shortage.         
